                    <floruit notBefore="1750" notAfter="1788">He was active sometime during the reign of <persName ref="PRS9153TaklaHa"/> (r. 1769–1777) up to <persName ref="PRS5618IyasuII">ʾIyāsu III</persName> (r. 1784 –1788). 
                        According to a record in <ref type="mss" corresp="ESdd044#a10"/>, he, together with <persName ref="PRS15130FessehaS"/>, <persName ref="PRS15132AnqasaHay"/>, <persName ref="PRS15137FessehaSey"/> 
                            and other monks, initiated the restoration of the monastery after it was destroyed by an earthquake in 1784.</floruit>
                </person>
